<p>运行我 Github 中的这个 <a href="https://github.com/MorvanZhou/Reinforcement-learning-with-tensorflow/blob/master/contents/5.2_Prioritized_Replay_DQN/run_MountainCar.py" target="_blank">MountainCar 脚本</a>,
